quran[5{c,v,t}:
5,104,aur jab un logon se kaha jata hai ke jo ( kitaab ) khuda ne nazil farmai hai is ki aur rasool allah ki taraf rujoo karo to kehte hain ke jis tareeq par hum ne apne baap dada ko paaya hai wohi hamein kaafi hai bhala agar un ke baap dada nah to kuch jantay hon aur nah seedhay raste par hon ( tab bhi? )
5,105,ae imaan walo! apni jaanun ki hifazat karo jab tum hadaayat par ho to koi gumraah tumhara kuch bhi bigaar nahi sakta tum sab ko khuda ki taraf lout kar jana hai is waqt woh tum ko tumahray sab kamon se jo ( duniya mein ) kiye they aagah kere ga ( aur un ka badla day ga )
5,106,momino! jab tum mein se kisi ki mout aa maujood ho to shahadat ( ka nisaab ) yeh hai ke wasiyat ke waqt tum ( musalmanoon ) mein se do adil ( yani sahib aitbaar ) gawah hon ya agar ( musalman nah milein aur ) tum safar kar rahay ho aur ( is waqt ) tum par mout ki museebat waqay ho to kisi dosray mazhab ke do ( shakhson ko ) gawah ( kar lau ) agar tum ko un gawahoon ki nisbat kuch shak ho to un ko ( asar ki ) namaz ke baad khara karo aur dono khuda ki kasmain khayen ke hum shahadat ka kuch aiwz nahi len ge go hamara rishta daar hi ho aur nah hum allah ki shahadat ko chupayen ge agar aisa karen ge to gunehgaar hon ge
5,107,phir agar maloom ho jaye ke un dono ne ( jhoot bol kar ) gunah haasilkiya hai to jin logon ka unhon ne haq maarna chaha tha un mein se un ki jagah aur do gawah kharray hon jo ( maiyat se ) qaraabat قریبہ rakhtay hon phir woh khuda ki kasmain khayen ke hamari shahadat un ki shahadat se bohat achi hai aur hum ne koi zayad-ti nahi ki aisakiya ho to hum be insaaf hain
5,108,is tareeq se bohat qareeb hai ke yeh log sahih sahih shahadat den ya is baat se khauf karen ke ( hamari ) kasmain un ki qasmon ke baad radd kar di jayen gi aur khuda se daro aur is ke hukmon ko ( gosh hosh se ) suno aur khuda nafarman logon ko hadaayat nahi deta
